WEBVTT

00:02:58.736 --> 00:03:00.314
kwa sababu hii michoro itaishi

00:03:00.314 --> 00:03:03.091
mda mrefu zaidi ya miili yetu.

00:03:03.091 --> 00:03:04.982
Na kama ni kweli, tunachotaka kufanya

00:03:04.982 --> 00:03:08.391
ni tunataka kupitia mambo manne kutoka kwa
Wagiriki

00:03:08.391 --> 00:03:11.700
na jambo moja kutoka kwa Mmarekani
wa Kusini.

00:03:11.700 --> 00:03:13.523
Kwanini Wagiriki?

00:03:13.523 --> 00:03:15.380
Wagiriki walifikiria kitakachotokea

00:03:15.380 --> 00:03:20.338
pale miungu na binadamu na ukosefu wa
maadili ukijichanganya kwa mda mrefu.

00:03:20.338 --> 00:03:23.018
Hivyo somo la kwanza: Sisyphus.

00:03:23.018 --> 00:03:26.044
Unakumbuka? Alifanya kitu kibaya,
kuhukumiwa kwa siku zote

00:03:26.044 --> 00:03:28.427
kupandisha hili jiwe juu, litarudi
tena chini,

00:03:28.427 --> 00:03:30.400
viringisha juu, viringika chini.